OL,5, Southern Water bosses have opted not to
OL,6, take bonuses following criticism of the
OL,7, company's sewage discharge record.     
OL,9,FThe company has faced calls from       
OL,10,Fcampaigners not to award bonuses until 
OL,11,Fsea water quality improved.            
OL,13,FChief executive Lawrence Gosden and    
OL,14,Fchief financial officer Stuart Ledger  
OL,15,Fhave both declined a bonus for the year
OL,16,Fto March 2023, the company announced in
OL,17,Fits annual report.                     
OL,19,F"We know that we have more to do," Mr  
OL,20,FGosden said.                           
